Description:
 Key AccountabilitiesWork with the Bot Controller and Business to Design optimal process automation solutions using different automation technologies. (the RPA Developer will be more involved in solution design based on the complexity of the solution, especially when tech like IQBot, OCR, ML, NLP,….. are involved);
Develop, test and deploy automated solutions that meets the Business’ requirements;
Ongoing support and maintenance of the automated solutions within production (assist the Bot Controller with the more complicated errors/exceptions);
EUCT (macro) development and maintenance;
Peer review Solution Designs to provide input into any potential shortcomings within the solution design;
Peer review RPA solutions build by other RPA developers to provide input to how the solutions can be improved, or identify code not adhering to the RPA development standards);
R&D new process automation technologies, and work with the team to institutionalize new process automation services;
Ongoing evolving of the RPA Framework (Bot Development Lifecycle, templates, governance and standards).Skills
